<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Oxley well. I understand the buyer profile that this suburb attracts and how to position a property to generate genuine competition in this market.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Oxley Station on the Ipswich/Springfield rail line provides one of the western corridor's most reliable CBD commute options, with trains arriving in the city in around 25 minutes. Buyers who have been priced out of Corinda and Sherwood consistently look to Oxley as the next credible option on the corridor. The suburb's 1950s-to-1970s housing stock on reasonable blocks suits the renovation activity that has lifted prices in comparable suburbs across Brisbane's south-west. Streets closest to the station attract the broadest buyer pool, and investor-grade stock is strong here, with rental demand sustained by the commuter demographic and the value gap that still exists relative to those established inner addresses.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Rail Access</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Ipswich/Springfield line</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Affordable Entry</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Established family suburb</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/corinda" style="color:#b98229;">Corinda</a>, <a href="/suburbs/sherwood" style="color:#b98229;">Sherwood</a>, <a href="/suburbs/graceville" style="color:#b98229;">Graceville</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION: FAQ
